### Damped Lissajous

Combine two-axis oscillation with exponential decay. The figure-eight collapses inward.

```scheme
(define (damped-fig8-x t)
  (* 60
     (exp (* -0.3 t))
     (sin (* t 2))))

(define (damped-fig8-y t)
  (* 60
     (exp (* -0.3 t))
     (sin (* t 4))))

(motion
  (on-wake
    (spawn
      (disk 8 \"amber\")
      (transform
        (at (damped-fig8-x (elapsed))
            (damped-fig8-y (elapsed)))))))
```

[VISUAL: Amber disk tracing a shrinking figure-eight, energy draining until it rests at the origin.]

