### Rotation + Translation Pendulum

A square swinging horizontally *and* rotating in sync. Position and angle share a phase.

```scheme
(define (swing-x t)
  (* 60 (sin (* t 2))))

(define (swing-angle t)
  (* 0.5 (sin (* t 2))))

(motion
  (on-wake
    (spawn
      (square 25 \"crimson\")
      (transform
        (at (swing-x (elapsed)) 0)
        (angle (swing-angle (elapsed)))))))
```

[VISUAL: Crimson square swinging left-right while tilting in the same rhythm—a coordinated dance.]

