### Vertical Chain (Three Springs)

Three disks vertically stacked, each driven by a phase-shifted sine. A soft chain.

```scheme
(define (chain-y t phase)
  (* 25 (sin (+ (* t 4) phase))))

(motion
  (on-wake
    (spawn
      (disk 8 \"gold\")
      (transform
        (at 0 (chain-y (elapsed) 0))))
    (spawn
      (disk 8 \"orange\")
      (transform
        (at 0 (+ -30 (chain-y (elapsed) 1.0)))))
    (spawn
      (disk 8 \"red\")
      (transform
        (at 0 (+ -60 (chain-y (elapsed) 2.0)))))))
```

[VISUAL: Three disks in a vertical stack, each bobbing with a slight lag—top disk leads, bottom disk trails, a ripple down the chain.]

