### Spirograph-Like Path (Two Circular Motions)

Large circle + small circle offset. Disk orbits the orbit.

```scheme
(define (spiro-x t)
  (+ (* 50 (cos (* t 1)))
     (* 20 (cos (* t 5)))))

(define (spiro-y t)
  (+ (* 50 (sin (* t 1)))
     (* 20 (sin (* t 5)))))

(motion
  (on-wake
    (spawn
      (disk 5 \"violet\")
      (transform
        (at (spiro-x (elapsed))
            (spiro-y (elapsed)))))))
```

[VISUAL: Violet disk looping in a spirograph pattern, a dense intricate path with lobes and cusps.]

