### Breathing Square (Oscillating Width and Height Independently)

A rectangle whose width and height pulse at different rates.

```scheme
(define (breathing-w t)
  (+ 40 (* 15 (sin (* t 3)))))

(define (breathing-h t)
  (+ 30 (* 10 (sin (* t 5)))))

(motion
  (on-wake
    (spawn
      (rectangle (breathing-w (elapsed))
                 (breathing-h (elapsed))
                 \"lime\")
      (transform))))
```

[VISUAL: Lime rectangle swelling and shrinking asymmetrically, width and height out of sync—an organic breathing shape.]

