### Beating Frequencies (Two Close Frequencies)

Two disks oscillating at nearly the same rate. Their combined motion \"beats\"—alternating constructive and destructive interference.

```scheme
(define (beat1 t)
  (* 40 (sin (* t 5.0))))

(define (beat2 t)
  (* 40 (sin (* t 5.3))))

(motion
  (on-wake
    (spawn
      (disk 8 \"orange\")
      (transform
        (at (beat1 (elapsed)) -15)))
    (spawn
      (disk 8 \"yellow\")
      (transform
        (at (beat2 (elapsed)) 15)))))
```

[VISUAL: Orange and yellow disks swinging vertically, sometimes in sync (both high together), sometimes out of sync—slow envelope modulation.]

