(define (chirp-x t)
  (* 60 (sin (* t t 0.5))))

(motion
  (on-wake
    (spawn
      (disk 10 \"cyan\")
      (transform
        (at (chirp-x (elapsed)) 0)))))
```

[VISUAL: Cyan disk swinging left-right, slowly at first, then accelerating into a rapid blur—a frequency sweep.]

